{"tid":520240,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"世界紀錄「最多毛女孩」　修髮剃毛露出真面目","createTime":"2018-01-05T08:19:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-29T08:24:03.000Z","uid":75969,"like":11,"dislike":319,"uniUserReply":119,"replies":[{"pid":"aca3faa6e13f127ae20847d02ca49c142e4280db","tid":520240,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T08:19:12.000Z","msg":"2010年曾獲《金氏世界紀錄》(Guinness World Record)認證為「世界最多毛女孩」(World's Hairiest Girl)的泰國女子素素樊(Sumatra Susuphan)，日前在個人《臉書》公布了一張洋溢著幸福的照片，照片中的她已將滿臉的長毛修去，露出「真面目」，並開心地與自己的「真命天子」合影。<br />\n<br />\n素素樊出生後就比一般嬰兒「長毛」，全身上下的毛髮不斷增生，特別是臉部與胸、背部，醫師診斷後證實她罹患了罕見的遺傳疾病「安布拉斯症候群」(Ambras Syndrome，又稱「狼人症候群」Werewolf Syndrome)，全身上下會不斷增生毛髮，這被視為一種「返祖現象」，與染色體的重新排列有關，罹病率僅有10億分之一，自中世紀以來在歷史上僅有50個案例，而素素樊是其中少數臉部也長滿毛髮的，雖然有醫師曾替她進行雷射除毛，但完全無用，仍然不斷長出新的毛髮。2010年時她才10歲，就獲得了《金氏世界紀錄》認證，成為「最多毛女孩」。<br />\n<br />\n雖然全身長滿毛髮讓素素樊的生活十分不方便，她甚至不敢到泳池游泳，但日前她在自己的《臉書》公布了幾張從未出現過的「真面目」照片，她表示，自己的症狀絲毫沒有改善，但她特別將臉上所有的毛髮都剃除，因為她結婚了，素素樊特別提到自己的丈夫，「他不只是我的初戀，更是我今生最愛」。（於慶中／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180105/640_8d260039cdb8f23226e155f51575d304.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180105%2F640_8d260039cdb8f23226e155f51575d304.jpg&h=6ddf298c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n素素樊曾在節目中公開「修毛」。翻攝自《每日星報》<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180105/640_4a4036cc9a6f3156da07f8e08b6fa9c5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180105%2F640_4a4036cc9a6f3156da07f8e08b6fa9c5.jpg&h=7438e8bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n素素樊10歲時的模樣。翻攝自《每日郵報》<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180105/640_2ac9e9b0f57535d7f2bfb5dc5e8ef2df.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180105%2F640_2ac9e9b0f57535d7f2bfb5dc5e8ef2df.jpg&h=9f836a47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n素素樊與同學感情很好。翻攝自《每日郵報》<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180105/640_6348c758509876a39b4319402911dc14.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180105%2F640_6348c758509876a39b4319402911dc14.jpg&h=eea98107&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n素素樊剃毛前與老公合影。翻攝自《每日郵報》<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180105/640_b3002256bac4e2452c49f66adf5af6a9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180105%2F640_b3002256bac4e2452c49f66adf5af6a9.jpg&h=353435f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n素素樊終於剃掉臉上長毛。翻攝自《每日郵報》<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180105/640_0442a0144349903b8a4f5bba55a9c78a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180105%2F640_0442a0144349903b8a4f5bba55a9c78a.jpg&h=0d72b7ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n素素樊(左)與老公合影。翻攝自《每日星報》<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20180105/1272197/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20180105%2F1272197%2F&d=5eF4tT49bOmdx1L6XUUpv8VakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=c8a913cc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20180105%2F1272197%2F&h=fb6945ff\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20180105/1272197/</a>"},{"pid":"983ca840b67f12cebc50fbc25affbe42800a55e6","tid":520240,"uid":33864,"like":1374,"dislike":7,"score":1367,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T08:21:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://farm6.staticflickr.com/5660/21149772766_cc40d33112_o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffarm6.staticflickr.com%2F5660%2F21149772766_cc40d33112_o.jpg&h=14c8bcf9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6614ff6ce0579d4e3c56582b2479faa247927f9d","tid":520240,"uid":693,"like":18,"